  "explanation": "Use a hash map to map original nodes to their copies. Traverse twice: once to create nodes and once to set next/random pointers.",
  "answer": "def copyRandomList(head):\n    if not head: return None\n    mp = {}; cur = head\n    while cur:\n        mp[cur] = Node(cur.val); cur = cur.next\n    cur = head\n    while cur:\n        if cur.next: mp[cur].next = mp[cur.next]\n        if cur.random: mp[cur].random = mp[cur.random]\n        cur = cur.next\n    return mp[head]",
